                                        @mratings /5
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 text-sm selfRating">
                                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
